"title": "5088: David, character of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5088",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>David, although not perfect, is portrayed as a man and a king after God's own heart.</p>\n<h2>David's appearance and attributes</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:18\">1SA 16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:12\">1SA 16:12</a></p>\n<h2>David's characteristics</h2>\n<h3>His dependence upon God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam13:14\">1SA 13:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:2\">1SA 23:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:4\">1SA 23:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam23:9-1Sam23:13\">1SA 23:9–23:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1-Ps23:6\">PSA 23:1–23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:1-Ps34:7\">PSA 34:1–34:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:1-Ps54:4\">PSA 54:1–54:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:1-Ps62:2\">PSA 62:1–62:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps142:1-Ps142:7\">PSA 142:1–142:7</a></p>\n<h3>His trust in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:34-1Sam17:37\">1SA 17:34–17:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:40-1Sam17:51\">1SA 17:40–17:51</a></p>\n<h3>His loyalty to others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41-1Sam20:42\">1SA 20:41–20:42</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:1\">2SA 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:6-2Sam9:7\">2SA 9:6–9:7</a></p>\n<h3>His respect for those in authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam24:1-1Sam24:7\">1SA 24:1–24:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam26:1-1Sam26:25\">1SA 26:1–26:25</a></p>\n<h3>His deep humanity is evident in his paternal grief</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:32-2Sam18:33\">2SA 18:32–18:33</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:38-2Sam13:39\">2SA 13:38–13:39</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:5\">2SA 18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:1-2Sam19:7\">2SA 19:1–19:7</a></p>\n<h2>David's abilities</h2>\n<h3>He was a strategist and courageous commander</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:3-2Sam8:6\">2SA 8:3–8:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:34-1Sam17:47\">1SA 17:34–17:47</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:6-2Sam5:10\">2SA 5:6–5:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:17-2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:17–5:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:1\">2SA 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:13-2Sam8:14\">2SA 8:13–8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam27:5-1Sam27:11\">1SA 27:5–27:11</a></p>\n<h3>He was a musician and poet</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:1\">2SA 23:1</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:18\">1SA 16:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:23\">1SA 16:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:10\">1SA 18:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:9-1Sam19:10\">1SA 19:9–19:10</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:1\">2SA 22:1</a> parallel PSA 18:0 <em>He sang</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:7\">1CH 16:7</a>; ; PSA 3:0, PSA 34:0, PSA 51:0, PSA 52:0, PSA 54:0, PSA 63:0</p>\n<h3>He was a wise leader</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam8:15\">2SA 8:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:18-2Sam7:29\">2SA 7:18–7:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:14\">2SA 15:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:25-2Sam15:29\">2SA 15:25–15:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:32-2Sam15:36\">2SA 15:32–15:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:5-2Sam16:12\">2SA 16:5–16:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:18-2Sam19:29\">2SA 19:18–19:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam21:1-2Sam21:9\">2SA 21:1–21:9</a></p>\n<h3>His military activities prevented him from building the temple</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:3\">1KI 5:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:7-1Chr22:8\">1CH 22:7–22:8</a></p>\n<h2>David's sin and repentance</h2>\n<h3>His adultery with Bathsheba and murder of Uriah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:2-2Sam11:4\">2SA 11:2–11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:7-2Sam12:10\">2SA 12:7–12:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:14-2Sam11:17\">2SA 11:14–11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam11:26-2Sam11:27\">2SA 11:26–11:27</a></p>\n<h3>His repentance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam12:13-2Sam12:23\">2SA 12:13–12:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:1-Ps51:19\">PSA 51:1–51:19</a></p>",
